381	1. AppBar back button
382	2. Progress Chart (entire card)
383	3. Toggle chips (in order 1W → 1M → All)
384	4. Latest Entry card
385	5. Nutrition Tips card
386	6. Weight Log list items (in order)
387	7. FAB
388	
389	### Contrast Notes
390	
391	- `lavenderBloom` on white: ~5.2:1 (passes AA)
392	- `deepGraphite` on morningMist: ~12:1 (passes AAA)
393	- `stoneGrey` on white: ~4.7:1 (passes AA for body text)
394	- `softMint` on morningMist: ~4.5:1 (passes AA for positive delta)
395	- `softCoral` on morningMist: ~4.8:1 (passes AA for negative delta/errors)
396	
397	### Screen Reader Support
398	
399	- Announce weight logging success: "Weight entry saved"
400	- Announce deletion: "Weight entry deleted"
401	- Announce chart range change: "Showing ${range} data"
402	- Use `Semantics` to label chart data points
403	
404	### Touch Target Compliance
405	
406	- All interactive elements: 48dp minimum
407	- FAB: 56dp (exceeds minimum)
408	- Toggle chips: 32dp height, 12dp horizontal padding (exceeds minimum)
409	- Log items: Full card tap, 56dp+ height
410	- All buttons: 48dp minimum height
411	
412	---
413	
414	## 11. Anti-Patterns
415	
416	**Do Not:**
417	- Use `GridView` for weight log list (simple `SliverList` is appropriate)
418	- Add bottom navigation (per UX spec, BottomNavigationBar is hidden)
419	- Use hard-coded weight units (read from `UserPreferences.units`)
420	- Place FAB in bottom center (bottom-right per design system)
421	- Show FAB on initial load without animation (fade-in over 200ms)
422	- Use pure black text on white/morningMist backgrounds
423	- Use Inter, Roboto, or any font other than Nunito
424	- Add shadows to AppBar (transparent/floating style)
425	- Use `Navigator.push` instead of `context.push` with GoRouter
426	- Skip safe area handling for FAB position
427	- Display empty state without illustration/guidance text
428	- Show negative delta styling for zero delta (use stoneGrey instead)
429	- Use generic chart colors not in the design system palette
