n- Checkbox, Radio, Switch\n- Slider, RangeSlider\n- DatePicker, TimePicker\n- SearchBar, SearchAnchor\n\n### Calls to Action\n- ElevatedButton, FilledButton, FilledButton.tonal\n- OutlinedButton, TextButton\n- FloatingActionButton, FloatingActionButton.extended\n- IconButton, CloseButton, BackButton\n\n### Feedback\n- SnackBar, MaterialBanner\n- CircularProgressIndicator, LinearProgressIndicator\n- RefreshIndicator\n- Shimmer (skeleton loading)\n- Badge, Tooltip\n\n### Layout\n- Scaffold, SafeArea\n- Column, Row, Wrap, Stack\n- Expanded, Flexible, Spacer\n- SizedBox, Padding, Center, Align\n- ConstrainedBox, AspectRatio\n\n## Adjective Palettes\n\n### Minimal / Clean\n- generous EdgeInsets, breathing room\n- surfaceContainerLowest backgrounds\n- subtle outlineVariant borders\n- single-weight typography\n\n### Professional / Corporate\n- neutral ColorScheme seed\n- consistent elevation hierarchy\n- structured GridView layouts\n- monospace labelSmall for data\n\n### Playful / Fun\n- vibrant primary seed color\n- large radiusLg on cards\n- Curves.elasticOut animations\n- bold headlineLarge weights\n\n### Dark Mode\n- dark ColorScheme brightness\n- surfaceContainer for elevation\n- high-contrast onSurface text\n- subtle outline borders\n\n## Color Role Terminology (Material 3)\n\n### Surfaces\n- `surface` — default background\n- `surfaceContainer` — slightly elevated\n- `surfaceContainerHigh` — more elevated\n- `surfaceContainerHighest` — most elevated\n- `inverseSurface` — inverted for contrast\n\n### Content\n- `onSurface` — primary text\n- `onSurfaceVariant` — secondary text\n- `outline` — borders, dividers\n- `outlineVariant` — subtle borders\n\n### Accent\n- `primary` — brand, CTAs, active states\n- `secondary` — supporting accent\n- `tertiary` — complementary accent\n- `error` — destructive, validation errors\n","numLines":95,"startLine":1,"totalLines":95}}}
